title: Seating unit

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for a seating unit, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a front left perspective view of a seating unit showing my new design embodied as a chair;
FIG. 2 is a back right perspective view thereof;
FIG. 3 is a front elevation view thereof;
FIG. 4 is a back elevation view thereof;
FIG. 5 is a left side elevation view thereof, the right side elevation being a mirror image thereof; and
FIG. 6 is a top plan view thereof; and
FIG. 7 is a front left perspective view of a seating unit showing my new design embodied as a loveseat;
FIG. 8 is a front elevation view thereof; and
FIG. 9 is a front left perspective view of a seating unit showing my new design embodied as a sofa; and,
FIG. 10 is a front elevation view thereof.
